These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, pall-mall
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, aquamarine, orange
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, musician, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, climbing
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the dressmaker is the person who likes orange##1
5. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes orange##1
7. the police-officer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar      | pall-mall  | ritmeester       | swisher   |
| Color          | orange | black | aquamarine |
| Job         | dressmaker  | police-officer | musician    |
| Sport   | climbing | swimming       | basketball      |

