.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, may
House: wooden, futuristic, cottage
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, tram, ship
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, documentary, drama
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the wooden house is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Birthday          | april      | november  | may        |
| House         | cottage | futuristic | wooden |
| Transport   | airplane | tram | ship       |
| Movie-Genre           | drama     | documentary     | family      |

