.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
House: ranch-style, colonial, craftsman
3 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, rat
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, brazilian, german
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, light-blue, red
1. the owner of the rat is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the german is in the middle##1
5. the russian is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
6. the craftsman house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| House      | colonial    | ranch-style        | craftsman |
| Pet           | lizard    | rat | mouse    |
| Nationality   | russian | german             | brazilian  |
| Color     | red     | lavender                | light-blue  |

