.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, quad-bike
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, swisher, chaman
House: tower, art-deco, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the tower house is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Transport          | taxi    | quad-bike  | snowmobile      |
| Cigar           | chaman    | davidoff | swisher |
| House   | townhouse   | art-deco  | tower     |
| Birthday   | march | february    | october      |

