.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, fanta
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, quad-bike, car
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, sunflower
3 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, whist
1. the person who growsiris is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person driving the car is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
5. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking water##1
6. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the train##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage         | fanta | water     | hot-chocolate   |
| Transport           | car       | quad-bike   | train     |
| Flower   | tulip     | iris | sunflower |
| Game           | whist      | backgammon         | monopoly  |

