3. the modern house is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
6. the wooden house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| House       | modern            | tower      | wooden  |
