2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Food           | broccoli | asparagus         | radish |
| Color   | white      | ivory | yellow     |
| Birthday   | june   | september       | december     |
| Sport           | skiing    | soccer         | snowboarding        |

