There 3 different types of food: artichoke, pepper, radish
1. the person eating radish is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
