.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
3 different games are played: go, bridge, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, alhambra
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, animation, thriller
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, black
1. the person who likes black is the person playing go##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Game         | bridge | go | backgammon   |
| Cigar           | alhambra     | montecristo    | ritmeester   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation         | thriller    | horror   |
| Color         | turquise       | black | coral |

