1. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the fan of disco##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Flower    | iris | begonia     | bellflower      |
| Game        | backgammon | poker       | monopoly |
| Music-Genre       | rock | disco | funk  |
| Pet   | goldfish    | snake   | chinchilla  |

