.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, june
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, cat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, vegafina
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, hiking
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday      | june      | may    | august    |
| Pet          | cat         | ferret    | hedgehog   |
| Cigar           | cain | vegafina | pall-mall |
| Hobby   | hiking         | fishing     | magic-tricks    |

