3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, horrorcher
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bolivar, tiparillo
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, mauve, lilac
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who likes green##1
2. the owner of the horrorcher is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes green##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is the person watching musical movies##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who likes green##1
6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | musical         | horror     | drama     |
| Pet           | hedgehog        | horrorcher | dog |
| Cigar   | bolivar        | tiparillo   | alhambra    |
| Color         | lilac | green   | mauve |

