.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, scooter
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, soy-milk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, azalea
1. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| City          | prague     | liverpool    | marseilles    |
| Transport         | motorbike | scooter | tram     |
| Beverage   | cola  | lemonade      | soy-milk        |
| Flower         | daisy   | rose   | azalea |

 